        {
          "name": "top_text",
          "value": "Losing a loved one can feel very overwhelming. Here are a few practical tips that can be helpful to keep in mind.",
          "_translations": {
            "value": {}
          },
          "type": "set_variable",
          "_nested_name": "bereavement_section.top_text"
        },
        {
          "name": "title_1",
          "value": "Ask for help",
          "_translations": {
            "value": {}
          },
          "type": "set_variable",
          "_nested_name": "bereavement_section.title_1"
        },
        {
          "name": "title_2",
          "value": "Say goodbye",
          "_translations": {
            "value": {}
          },
          "type": "set_variable",
          "_nested_name": "bereavement_section.title_2"
        },
        {
          "name": "text_1",
          "value": "- Ask someone you trust for help - food or childcare can be useful. You may need documents for inheritance, for your children, or to access services.\n- Sometimes people try to take money or inheritance from a grieving person. Find out about your rights.",
          "_translations": {
            "value": {}
          },
          "type": "set_variable",
          "_nested_name": "bereavement_section.text_1"
        },
        {
          "name": "text_2",
          "value": "- Saying goodbye is difficult. Do what feels okay for you and your teen. \n- Families, teens and parents are not perfect. When someone has died, it is okay to talk about the good and bad things we remember. \n- It can help to write a letter or make a drawing for the person who has gone.  \n- Some people hold a ceremony or have a special meal to celebrate the person, and say goodbye.  \n- It can help to make a box of memories, to put things that remind you and your teen of the person.  \n- It can help just to talk about the person when you think about them.",
          "_translations": {
            "value": {}
          },
          "type": "set_variable",
          "_nested_name": "bereavement_section.text_2"
        }
      ],
      "_nested_name": "bereavement_section"
    }
